{"id":602201,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/12/【立此存照】坚决防止批评性报道集中出现/","date":"2018-12-24T08:19:24Z","modified":"2018-12-24T08:19:24Z","title":"【立此存照】坚决防止批评性报道集中出现","content":"<p>12月24日，社交媒体上网友热传一张“关于加强社会类、娱乐类新闻节目管理通知”的PPT现场讲解照片，疑似官方媒体内部培训内容流出，图片右下角疑有“CNR 央广传媒”（猜测）字样。</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>坚持团结稳定鼓励、正面宣传为主</strong></p>\n<p>坚决防止批评性报道在一定时期内集中于一个地区或行业；不要公开批评报道现阶段暂时解决不了的问题和有关地方、部门已经依法处理解决的问题；</p>\n<p>不要跨区域进行舆论监督采访报道。</p></blockquote>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-602213\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/DvJwx-bUwAEwVCj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/DvJwx-bUwAEwVCj.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/DvJwx-bUwAEwVCj-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/DvJwx-bUwAEwVCj-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><span id=\".E5.BE.B7.E5.9B.BD.E4.B9.8B.E5.A3.B0_.7C_.E6.9C.BA.E6.9E.84.E6.94.B9.E9.9D.A9.EF.BC.9A.E4.B8.AD.E5.AE.A3.E9.83.A8.E7.9B.B4.E6.8E.A5.E7.AE.A1.E7.90.86.E6.96.B0.E9.97.BB.E5.87.BA.E7.89.88.E5.92.8C.E7.94.B5.E5.BD.B1\" class=\"mw-headline\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9B%BD%E4%B9%8B%E5%A3%B0-%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%AE%A3%E9%83%A8%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E5%92%8C/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\">德国之声 | 机构改革：中宣部直接管理新闻出版和电影</a></span></p>\n<p><span id=\".E4.BA.BA.E6.B0.91.E6.97.A5.E6.8A.A5.EF.BD.9C1100.E5.A4.9A.E4.B8.AA.E5.A4.A7V.E8.B4.A6.E5.8F.B7.E8.A2.AB.E5.85.B3.E9.97.AD\" class=\"mw-headline\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/12/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5%EF%BD%9C1100%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E5%A4%A7v%E8%B4%A6%E5%8F%B7%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow no